      "author": "SteveOverSea",
      "description": "The biggest internal refactor so far! :partying_face: \r\n\r\nThe plugin now uses `Decoration.mark()` instead of `Decoration.widget()` which allows now for a moving cursor when in any editing mode!\r\n\r\nAlso a new feature was added, **support for the outgoing links tab**:\r\n- resolved folder links behave the same as internal links\r\n- if not resolved, a new folder will be created (which mirrors exactly the internal link behavior)\r\n- also the icon for an unresolved link in the outgoing links tab was adjusted!\r\n\r\nHope I didn't introduce too much bugs with this big update! :rocket:  \r\n\r\nHave fun!",
